    "description": "<p>A protective magical force surrounds you, manifesting as spectral flames that covers you and your gear. You emit Light in a 2 Space Radius.</p>\n<p>Make a <strong>DC 15 Spell Check</strong>.</p>\n<p><strong>Success:</strong> You gain 3 Temp HP.</p>\n<p><strong>Success (each 5):</strong> +1 Temp HP.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure:</strong> 2 Temp HP.</p>\n<p>If a&nbsp;creature hits you with a <strong>Melee Attack </strong>while you have this <strong>Temp HP</strong>, the creature takes 1 <strong>Fire </strong>damage for each Temp HP it consumes with its Attack. The Spell ends once the Temp HP is consumed.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Mana Point Enhancements</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Fire Protection: (3 MP) </strong>Gain <strong>Fire Resist </strong>and add 10 more Temp HP.</li>\n<li><strong>Investiture of Fire: (5 MP, 1 AP) </strong>Gain <strong>Fire Immunity</strong>&nbsp;and add 15 more Temp HP. <br>Additionally while you have this Temp HP you can spend <strong>2 AP</strong> shoot out flames in a 3 Space Cone. Make a <strong>Spell Check </strong>against all creatures in the spells range&rsquo;s PD. <br><strong>Hit:</strong> The target takes <strong>5</strong> <strong>Fire </strong>damage.</li>\n</ul>",
